# shadcn/ui v4 Patterns

## Button as Link
shadcn v4 uses Base UI, NOT Radix. There is **no `asChild` prop**. Never use `render={<Link>}` on Button either — it triggers a `nativeButton` warning.

```tsx
// ❌ BAD — will error
<Button asChild><Link href="/foo">Go</Link></Button>
<Button render={<Link href="/foo" />}>Go</Button>

// ✅ GOOD — use buttonVariants on Link directly
import { buttonVariants } from "@/components/ui/button";
import { cn } from "@/lib/utils";

<Link href="/foo" className={cn(buttonVariants({ variant: "outline", size: "sm" }))}>
  Go
</Link>
```

## Adding Components
```bash
npx shadcn@latest add [component-name]
```
Components land in `src/components/ui/`. Do not manually edit them.

## Tailwind v4
Use `bg-linear-to-r` instead of `bg-gradient-to-r`. The old syntax still works but triggers lint warnings.
